


==============LINUX====================


./configure --help
./configure 
make 
sudo make install

to get the docs into assistant type:
assistant -addContentFile /usr/share/doc/libqxt/index.dcf



==============WINDOWS-mingw====================



./configure.bat
make 
make install

to get the docs into assistant type:
assistant -addContentFile C:\libqxt\doc\libqxt\index.dcf


==============WINDOWS-msvc====================


./configure.bat -msvc
nmake 
nmake install

to get the docs into assistant type:
assistant -addContentFile C:\libqxt\doc\libqxt\index.dcf

